        "start": 1.149,
        "end": 2.232,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C2-1",
    "durationFrames": 176,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C2-1.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Meet Martin.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 0.928,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Twenty years on the desk.",
        "start": 0.928,
        "end": 2.464,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "His first rule: read the client before you touch the product.",
        "start": 2.464,
        "end": 5.809000000000001,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C2-2",
    "durationFrames": 173,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C2-2.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Two basic moves.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.523,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "A call is the right to buy at a fixed price.",
        "start": 1.523,
        "end": 4.13,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "A put is the right to sell.",
        "start": 4.13,
        "end": 5.714,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C2-3",
    "durationFrames": 222,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C2-3.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Neither right is free.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.662,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "You pay a premium.",
        "start": 1.662,
        "end": 2.798,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Think of a movie ticket: buy it, you're in.",
        "start": 2.798,
        "end": 5.206,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Movie's terrible?",
        "start": 5.206,
        "end": 6.284,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "No refunds!",
        "start": 6.284,
        "end": 7.35,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C2-4",
    "durationFrames": 248,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C2-4.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Here's the call's payoff.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.452,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Flat, flat, flat, then up.",
        "start": 1.452,
        "end": 3.142,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Below the strike you lose only the ticket price.",
        "start": 3.142,
        "end": 6.357,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Above it, you participate.",
        "start": 6.357,
        "end": 8.226,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C2-5",
    "durationFrames": 36,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C2-5.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "The put is the mirror.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.297,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "It pays when the market falls.",
        "start": 1.297,
        "end": 1.297,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Insurance, basically.",
        "start": 1.297,
        "end": 1.297,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C2-6",
    "durationFrames": 176,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C2-6.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "First client.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.119,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Miz Li.",
        "start": 1.119,
        "end": 2.035,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "She's bullish on the index, but she cannot stomach a big loss.",
        "start": 2.035,
        "end": 5.833,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C2-7",
    "durationFrames": 232,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C2-7.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Four shelves.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.059,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Vanilla call.",
        "start": 1.059,
        "end": 2.059,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Vanilla put.",
        "start": 2.059,
        "end": 3.19,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Buy the index outright.",
        "start": 3.19,
        "end": 4.654,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "And a locked barrier product, we'll earn that one later.",
        "start": 4.654,
        "end": 7.678,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C2-8",
    "durationFrames": 114,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C2-8.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Bullish view, plus capped downside?",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.897,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "That's a vanilla call.",
        "start": 1.897,
        "end": 3.113,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Click.",
        "start": 3.113,
        "end": 3.75,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C2-9",
    "durationFrames": 291,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C2-9.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Before he signs, disclosure.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 2.13,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "If the option expires worthless, the entire premium is gone.",
        "start": 2.13,
        "end": 6.023,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "We say it out loud.",
        "start": 6.023,
        "end": 7.226,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Compliance is not decoration.",
        "start": 7.226,
        "end": 9.63,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C2-10",
    "durationFrames": 226,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C2-10.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Now the market runs.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.404,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Twenty-one five.",
        "start": 1.404,
        "end": 2.69,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Twenty-two one.",
        "start": 2.69,
        "end": 3.797,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Twenty-two four at expiry.",
        "start": 3.797,
        "end": 6.023,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "The call lands in the money.",
        "start": 6.023,
        "end": 7.488,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C2-11",
    "durationFrames": 246,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C2-11.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "But look at the net line.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.226,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Payoff minus premium.",
        "start": 1.226,
        "end": 2.833,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Direction right is not enough, you have to out-earn the ticket price.",
        "start": 2.833,
        "end": 6.964,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Remember that number.",
        "start": 6.964,
        "end": 8.154,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C2-12",
    "durationFrames": 263,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C2-12.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "And in the real contract, every point is fifty Hong Kong dollars.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 4.392,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Four hundred points of payoff is twenty thousand dollars.",
        "start": 4.392,
        "end": 7.595,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Per contract.",
        "start": 7.595,
        "end": 8.69,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-1",
    "durationFrames": 184,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-1.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Day two.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 0.869,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "New client, Mister Wang.",
        "start": 0.869,
        "end": 2.63,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "And today he wants a price.",
        "start": 2.63,
        "end": 4.309,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Not a feeling.",
        "start": 4.309,
        "end": 5.25,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "A number.",
        "start": 5.25,
        "end": 6.059,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-2",
    "durationFrames": 217,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-2.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Here's the secret nobody tells retail...",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 2.351,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "an option price is not guessed.",
        "start": 2.351,
        "end": 4.652,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "It is built!",
        "start": 4.652,
        "end": 5.613,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Branch, by branch.",
        "start": 5.613,
        "end": 7.175,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-3",
    "durationFrames": 105,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-3.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Start at today.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.0,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Index at twenty-one thousand five hundred.",
        "start": 1.0,
        "end": 3.452,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-4",
    "durationFrames": 293,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-4.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "One step ahead, two futures.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 2.321,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Up two point six five percent, or down two point five eight.",
        "start": 2.321,
        "end": 6.19,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "That spread comes from volatility, sixteen percent a year.",
        "start": 6.19,
        "end": 9.702,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-5",
    "durationFrames": 199,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-5.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "The up factor is e to the sigma root delta-t.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 4.14,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "The down factor is just one over it.",
        "start": 4.14,
        "end": 6.588,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-6",
    "durationFrames": 281,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-6.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "And the chance of going up, the risk-neutral probability, is e to the r delta-t minus d, over u minus d.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 7.981,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "That's the whole machine.",
        "start": 7.981,
        "end": 9.296,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-7",
    "durationFrames": 191,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-7.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Three steps to expiry.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.607,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Eight paths.",
        "start": 1.607,
        "end": 2.69,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Four final prices, from nineteen nine to twenty-three two.",
        "start": 2.69,
        "end": 6.309,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-8",
    "durationFrames": 230,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-8.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "At expiry the payoff is simple.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 2.154,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Final price minus strike of twenty-two thousand, or zero.",
        "start": 2.154,
        "end": 6.261,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Whichever is bigger.",
        "start": 6.261,
        "end": 7.595,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-9",
    "durationFrames": 264,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-9.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Then we walk backwards.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.535,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Each node is the discounted, probability-weighted average of its two children.",
        "start": 1.535,
        "end": 6.428,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Fold the future into the present.",
        "start": 6.428,
        "end": 8.738,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-10",
    "durationFrames": 217,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-10.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "And the tree hands us the answer: one hundred eighty-six points.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 4.11,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "That...",
        "start": 4.11,
        "end": 4.493375,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "is the theoretical price of this call.",
        "start": 4.493375,
        "end": 7.177,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-11",
    "durationFrames": 314,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-11.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Now the sales part.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.214,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Theory says one eighty-six.",
        "start": 1.214,
        "end": 3.511,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "The desk needs margin.",
        "start": 3.511,
        "end": 5.059,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Quote between plus four and plus thirty-four over theoretical and the client fills.",
        "start": 5.059,
        "end": 10.416,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-12",
    "durationFrames": 174,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-12.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Quote fat?",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.0,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "He walks to the bank across the street.",
        "start": 1.0,
        "end": 2.909,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Quote thin?",
        "start": 2.909,
        "end": 4.022,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "You just ate the risk for free.",
        "start": 4.022,
        "end": 5.738,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-13",
    "durationFrames": 210,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-13.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Two hundred ten.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.013,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Filled!",
        "start": 1.013,
        "end": 1.734,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "That spread between one eighty-six and two ten?",
        "start": 1.734,
        "end": 5.405,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "That's the desk's lunch.",
        "start": 5.405,
        "end": 6.914,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C3-14",
    "durationFrames": 202,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C3-14.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Market drifts to twenty-two one.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.928,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Small payoff, smaller than the premium.",
        "start": 1.928,
        "end": 4.392,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "The client learns.",
        "start": 4.392,
        "end": 5.75,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "So do you.",
        "start": 5.75,
        "end": 6.69,
        "words": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "C4-1",
    "durationFrames": 226,
    "audioSrc": "voiceover/edge/C4-1.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Day three.",
        "start": 0.05,
        "end": 1.166,
        "words": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Miz Chen.",
        "start": 1.166,
        "end": 2.166,
